<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.6.6">
<l>varuntā tirunī maṭaneñcē nammēl viṉaikaḷ vārāmuṉ</l>
<l>tiruntā varakkar teṉṉilaṅkai centī yuṇṇac civantorunāḷ</l>
<l>peruntōḷ vāṇaṟ karuḷpurintu piṉṉai maṇāḷa ṉākimuṉ</l>
<l>karuntāḷ kaḷiṟoṉ ṟocittāṉūr kaṇṇa puramnām toḻutumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Be without worry, simple heart! Karma will not pour down upon us.</l>
<l rend="indent">We will worship in Kaṇṇapuram,</l>
<l>The city of him who once broke [the tusk of] an elephant with dark feet,</l>
<l>Once raged so that blazing flames consumed</l>
<l rend="indent">the dishonorable demon’s Laṅkā of the south,</l>
<l>Bestowing grace on many-armed Bāṇa one day,</l>
<l rend="indent">and becoming Piṉṉai’s beloved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
